Package org.jboss.windup.ui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultValueAdapter<T>
    An adapter between ConfigurationOption.getDefaultValue() default values, and SingleValued.setDefaultValue(Callable)
    DistributionUpdater
    Performs the update of Windup distribution, currently by replacing a Windup directory with the content of a new Windup version offline distribution archive.
    RulesetUpdateChecker
    Upon the PostStartup CDI event, this checks whether a Windup core ruleset update is available.
    WindupCommand
    Provides a basic Forge UI implementation for running Windup from within a UIProvider.
    WindupProgressMonitorAdapter
    Progress monitor implementation based on the Forge/Eclipse progress monitor feature.
    WindupUpdateDistributionCommand
    Provides a basic UI command updating the whole windup distribution.
    WindupUpdateRulesetCommand
    Provides a basic UI command updating the rules/migration-core folder with the latest version.
